descriptionHtml:
NOTE: I Did not add Amidianborn Elven Armor texture to the download file, if you download this it will use the Vanilla Elven Armor Texture, read the Next note for more info... don\'t jump to conclusions...

Read the book in High Hrothgar (where the greybeards are at) :)
This is a pretty okay looking armor i have made based on an Angelic look/kinda overdone XD
i\'m sure its not everyone\'s style but i hope you love it!

NOTE: the texture i used is different the text i used on it was Amidianborn which was not meant to be apart of the armor on purpose it is by accident, so if you want your armor to look like mine then go here http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23125! I chose the Darker version but he/she has another one too. I haven\'t seen this with the regular texture so if you still use that then please post a pic :)
author: Me
